cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically object pose estimation from a single RGB image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of robots and manipulation suggests cs.RO (Robotics and Control) as another possible category. Finally, the paper involves matching and tracking objects, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
